| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2937 — Recovery Inhibition (apt73)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0dee0371-9f6d-5141-ac0d-f77062fc2b0c"
